.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-PAY-AMOUNT-TOTAL-MONTHLY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-pay-amount-total-monthly \- FEAT-2874 node-pay-amount-total-monthly
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-pay-amount-total-monthly
.SH DESCRIPTION
Total payment amount sent this calendar month (FEAT-2874).
.PP
Queries completed payments via lightning-cli listpays and sums amount_sent_msat
for entries whose completed_at timestamp falls within the current UTC calendar month.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
